        public boolean isDifferent(M wrappedObject)
        Determines if the value in the model object and the property field are different or not. This method is used to implement the ModelWrapper.differentProperty() flag.
        Parameters:
        wrappedObject - the wrapped model object
        Returns:
        false if both the wrapped model object and the property field have the same value, otherwise true
